; Coverage test for op.cc calc_cons
; Tests the O_CONS list construction operator.
; When a function is called with multiple arguments separated by commas,
; the arguments form a cons list that must be evaluated.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(justify(display_amount, 20, -1, true))\n'
              $50.00
             $-50.00
end test
